<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Raccoon App - Refund Policy</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/Logo3.webp" type="image/png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <style>
      /* General Page Styles */
      /* Full-page gradient background */
      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d001a, #1a0033 40%, #260044);
        background-attachment: fixed; /* Prevent seams while scrolling */
        background-size: cover;
        color: #fff;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      /* Main container with transparent/glass effect */
      .main-container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        background: rgba(
          20,
          0,
          40,
          0.8
        ); /* Slight transparency to let gradient show */
        backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.2);
      }

      /* Page title */
      .blogss {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        color: #ff00ff;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff00ff, 0 0 20px #9900ff;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }

      /* Headings with neon glow */
      h2 {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        margin-top: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: #00e5ff;
        text-shadow: 0 0 8px #00e5ff, 0 0 16px #00e5ff;
        border-left: 4px solid #ff00ff;
        padding-left: 10px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        color: #ddd;
      }

      /* Lists */
      ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      ul li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      /* Footer */
      footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 15px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.3);
        color: #fff;
        margin-top: 40px;
      }

      /* Links */
      a {
        color: #ff00ff;
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px #ff00ff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      a:hover {
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff00ff, 0 0 20px #ff00ff;
      }

      .ext {
        position: fixed;
        top: 1%;
        left: 3%;
        cursor: pointer;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d27bff, #b84bff);
        height: 50px;
        width: 50px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border-radius: 50%;
        transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      }

      .ext img {
        width: 60%;
        height: auto;
        transition: transform 0.25s ease-in-out;
      }

      /* Hover effects */
      .ext:hover {
        transform: scale(1.1);
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b84bff, #8f3aff);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      }

      .ext:hover img {
        transform: rotate(10deg);
      }

      /* Mobile Responsive */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .main-container {
          padding: 20px;
        }
        h2 {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .blogss {
          font-size: 1.6rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
    <main>
      <div class="main-container">
        <div class="action-container">
          <div onclick="window.location.href = '/'" class="blogss ext">
            <img src="/img/Home.png" width="32px" style="filter: invert(1)" />
          </div>
          <p class="blogss">REFUND POLICY</p>
          <div class="button-container" style="margin-top: 10%">
            <p>
              At <strong>Raccoon App</strong>, we strive to provide the best
              experience for our users. If you are not satisfied with our
              subscription service, you may be eligible for a partial refund as
              outlined below.
            </p>

            <h2>Subscription Cancellation & Refunds</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>
                You may cancel your subscription at any time from your account
                settings.
              </li>
              <li>
                If you cancel your subscription within "7 days of purchase", you
                will automatically receive a 50% refund.
              </li>
              <li>
                Refunds will be credited back to the original payment method.
              </li>
              <li>After "7 days", no refunds will be issued</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Non Refundable Situations</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>
                Refunds will not be issued for promotional or discounted
                subscriptions.
              </li>
              <li>
                Users who have violated our
                <a href="/terms-service">Terms of Use</a> will not be eligible
                for a refund.
              </li>
              <li>
                We do not provide refunds for technical issues that are beyond
                our control such as poor internet connection or third party
                software interference.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Refund Processing Time</h2>
            <p>
              Refunds are typically processed within 1-5 business days of your
              subscription cancellation.
            </p>

            <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>
              We reserve the right to update our refund policy at any time. Any
              changes will be reflected on this page. This policy was last
              modified on 24/06/25.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <script
      src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.4.min.js"
      integrity="sha256-oP6HI9z1XaZNBrJURtCoUT5SUnxFr8s3BzRl+cbzUq8="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <!-- <script src="/js/main.js"></script> -->
  </body>
</html>
